I"<h1 id="welcome-to-the-cardiff-society-for-industrial-and-applied-mathematics-siam-student-chapter">Welcome to the Cardiff Society for Industrial and Applied Mathematics (SIAM) Student Chapter!</h1>

<p>We organise various academic and social events for postgraduate students in Cardiff, including weekly seminars given by PhD students and a weekly ‘PGR tea at 3’.
We also organise various events such as the introductory poster presentation for welcoming new studtens, and the Three minute thesis competition.</p>
